=============
* Stage XX  *
=============

1. Description
--------------
pyDKB testing stage.

Run as:

  ./json2TTL.py -i input
  ./json2TTL.py input/196.json
  cat << EOF | ./json2TTL.py -m s | less
  {"a": 1}
  {"b": 2}
  EOF
  ./json2TTL.py --hdfs -i /my/test/input

etc

2. What to check
----------------

Test cases:

(+) in file mode with no parameters
    (expected: "no input file specified" error):

  ./json2TTL.py -m f

(+) without parameters
    (expeted: same as in file mode without parameters)

  ./json2TTL.py

(+) read input from file(s)
(+) output to (s)tream
    (expected: output file(s) content)

  ./json2TTL.py -d s input/NDjson.json
  ./json2TTL.py -d s input/NDjson.json input/NDjson.json

(+) read with wrong EOM
    (expected: can't decode message(s), works till the ens)

  ./json2TTL.py -d s input/EOMDjson.json
  ./json2TTL.py -d s -e EOM input/NDjson.json

(+) read with custom EOM from file(s)
    (expected: output file(s) content, re-formatted so that all JSONs
     are one-line)

  ./json2TTL.py -d s -e EOM input/EOMDjson.json && echo ''
  ./json2TTL.py -d s -e EOM input/EOMDjson.json input/EOMDjson.json && echo ''

(-) last message not ended with EOM
    (expected: last message is thrown away)

  ./json2TTL.py -d s -e EOM input/NDjson.json
